PC Number Date Chapter Bill Dept
 2023-06492023-06-22GAC
ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectOrder Authorizing the Canada-Brazil Framework Agreement concerning Defence Cooperation
PrecisOrder authorizing (1) the Prime Minister or the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign, on behalf of the Government of Canada, subject to ratification, the FRAMEWORK AGREEMENT BETWEEN THE GOVERNMENT OF CANADA AND THE GOVERNMENT OF BRAZIL CONCERNING DEFENCE COOPERATION; or (2) the Minister of Foreign Affairs to execute and issue an Instrument of Full Powers, authorizing the individuals mentioned in the order, to sign, on behalf of the Government of Canada, subject to ratification, the Agreement.
